WEBVTT

00:00.702 --> 00:02.295
MIKE:
<i>Previously on</i> Mike & Molly...

00:02.296 --> 00:04.313
MAN: Watch out!

00:05.868 --> 00:07.703
CARL:
<i>After that accident,</i>

00:07.704 --> 00:10.238
the one face that's been popping
up in my mind is Victoria's.

00:10.240 --> 00:11.973
Mike, I'm gonna ask her
to marry me.

00:11.975 --> 00:14.175
MIKE:
<i>He's gonna propose to Victoria.</i>

00:14.177 --> 00:16.178
He's gonna propose?
I didn't say anything.

00:16.178 --> 00:18.012
You said exactly that!
I know, I know, I know!

00:18.014 --> 00:19.047
But don't tell anybody.
Don't tell anybody.

00:19.048 --> 00:20.147
He wants it to be a surprise.

00:20.149 --> 00:21.549
You got the ring?
What ring?

00:21.551 --> 00:23.751
The ring you're gonna use
to propose to Victoria with.

00:23.753 --> 00:26.321
I changed my mind.
That ain't happening.

00:26.322 --> 00:27.723
Man. I cannot decide
what I want.

00:27.724 --> 00:29.724
God, you make me sick.

00:29.725 --> 00:31.293
What is going on?

00:31.294 --> 00:32.259
Nothing, sweetie.

00:32.261 --> 00:34.362
Unfortunately,
nothing is going on.

00:34.363 --> 00:36.731
Isn't that right, Carl?

00:36.732 --> 00:37.999
Victoria,

00:38.000 --> 00:39.401
I love you.

00:39.402 --> 00:40.702
I mean, I-I really do.

00:40.703 --> 00:42.571
And, you know,
one day, who knows?

00:42.572 --> 00:44.706
You know, but whatever
you thought was happening,

00:44.707 --> 00:46.041
not gonna happen.

00:46.042 --> 00:48.209
Oh, thank goodness.

00:48.210 --> 00:50.210
What's that now?

00:50.212 --> 00:52.280
Getting my stuff
and I'm getting out of here.

00:52.281 --> 00:53.682
Go ahead, be a baby.

00:53.683 --> 00:55.216
Need help changing
your diaper?!

00:55.217 --> 00:57.751
CARL: Oh, no, don't try
and get sexy with me!

01:00.795 --> 01:02.557
MIKE:
<i>Uh, yeah.</i>

01:02.558 --> 01:04.858
Yeah, about 30 people.
Saturday night.

01:04.860 --> 01:06.895
Okay, I'll e-mail you
my information.

01:06.896 --> 01:08.062
Thank you.

01:08.063 --> 01:09.063
Who was that?

01:09.064 --> 01:10.899
Ah, I've been
racking my brains

01:10.900 --> 01:12.165
trying to plan me and Molly's
anniversary party.

01:12.167 --> 01:13.735
Mm-hmm.
And then bam!

01:13.736 --> 01:15.803
A Dave & Buster's
commercial came on

01:15.804 --> 01:18.373
like a sign from God.

01:18.374 --> 01:21.943
God told you to have an
anniversary party at an arcade?

01:21.944 --> 01:24.111
And pub.

01:25.480 --> 01:27.582
Do you really think
Molly's idea of romance

01:27.583 --> 01:29.349
involves a plastic cup
full of tokens?

01:29.351 --> 01:31.786
It's not tokens, it's
a credit card that you sw...

01:31.787 --> 01:33.887
Have you not been there?

01:33.889 --> 01:35.923
Here's what you're gonna do:
you're gonna take Molly

01:35.924 --> 01:38.125
and your closest friends
on a moonlight dinner cruise

01:38.126 --> 01:39.192
of Lake Michigan.

01:39.194 --> 01:40.261
Okay? There's gonna be
some drinking,

01:40.262 --> 01:41.262
there's gonna be some dancing,

01:41.263 --> 01:42.630
and breathtaking views
of the city

01:42.631 --> 01:44.031
where you fell in love.

01:44.032 --> 01:46.366
Wow. That's good.

01:46.368 --> 01:48.369
Yeah. That's where
I was gonna take Victoria

01:48.370 --> 01:49.603
for our anniversary.

01:49.605 --> 01:51.472
Mm, sorry, buddy.
I feel for you.

01:51.473 --> 01:53.573
Hey, can you fish off that boat?

01:57.878 --> 01:59.245
Hey, Molly.

01:59.247 --> 02:01.983
Hey, Carl. Didn't think you'd...
still be here.

02:01.984 --> 02:04.951
Mike, I didn't think he'd still be here.
Yeah,

02:04.953 --> 02:06.854
I'm sorry. I didn't realize
the game was gonna go this long.

02:06.855 --> 02:09.122
(quietly): Can't you take Victoria around
the block a couple times?

02:09.124 --> 02:11.325
No, we already took
a couple extra hours at the spa.

02:11.326 --> 02:14.727
I've got stuff waxed
that shouldn't be waxed.

02:15.596 --> 02:16.964
Really?

02:16.965 --> 02:18.465
Just get him out.

02:18.466 --> 02:21.267
All right, hey, uh, Carl,
we got to wrap this up, buddy.

02:21.269 --> 02:23.470
How 'bout we listen to
the rest of the game in the car?

02:23.471 --> 02:24.605
What, basketball on the radio?

02:24.606 --> 02:26.440
That's just a bunch
of squeaky sneakers.

02:26.441 --> 02:28.241
You guys,

02:28.243 --> 02:30.044
I know Victoria's out
on the porch, all right?

02:30.045 --> 02:32.279
Just let her in.
We're both adults.

02:32.280 --> 02:34.548
No, you're not.

02:34.549 --> 02:36.784
I suppose this was gonna happen
at some point.

02:36.785 --> 02:38.752
What are you doing, silly?

02:38.753 --> 02:41.822
Oh. Hello.

02:41.823 --> 02:43.123
Victoria.

02:43.124 --> 02:45.025
Yeah. Uh, we were just going.

02:45.026 --> 02:46.860
Oh, you don't have
to go anywhere on my account.

02:46.861 --> 02:48.494
CARL:
See? We're fine.

02:48.496 --> 02:49.730
Let's just watch
the end of this game.

02:49.731 --> 02:51.698
And, Victoria, you
might want to join us.

02:51.699 --> 02:53.933
You like to play games.

02:54.935 --> 02:57.371
My favorite game was
Dump the Chump, so...

02:57.372 --> 02:58.372
Okay!

02:58.373 --> 02:59.640
Okay,

02:59.641 --> 03:01.641
we tried, we failed.

03:01.642 --> 03:03.743
Carl, maybe you should go.

03:03.745 --> 03:05.412
No, I'm here as a guest
of my best friend, all right?

03:05.413 --> 03:07.447
And if he wants me to leave,
he should just tell me himself.

03:07.448 --> 03:08.714
I want you to leave.

03:10.817 --> 03:12.785
No.
VICTORIA: Ugh.

03:12.787 --> 03:14.820
Why do you always to be
such a drama queen?

03:14.822 --> 03:17.489
(gasps)
Don't you dare call me that!

03:17.491 --> 03:19.592
I don't know
what I ever saw in you.

03:19.594 --> 03:20.894
You know what, well,
I got news for you, lady.

03:20.895 --> 03:22.596
You're not the first
woman to say that.

03:22.597 --> 03:24.531
You're an awful man!

03:24.532 --> 03:25.598
And you're a crazy woman!

03:25.600 --> 03:26.633
Ugh!
Okay! Okay!

03:26.634 --> 03:28.101
You get yours,
I'll get mine!

03:28.102 --> 03:29.035
All right, let's go.

03:29.036 --> 03:30.036
Just call him Daddy...

03:30.037 --> 03:31.303
he'll do whatever you want!

03:32.572 --> 03:35.240
I don't want to hear any more!
Just get Daddy out of here.

